# Brand Naming

- Use `ingame` only for internal identifiers and technical slugs:
  - repo/package names
  - bundle IDs, package IDs, URL schemes
  - image/chart/runtime names like `ingame-api` and `ingame-web`
- Use `InGame` for every user-visible product name:
  - app titles
  - launcher labels
  - browser tab titles
  - window titles
  - README/docs/product copy
- Use `in-game` only in domain and host contexts such as `https://in-game.app`.
- Do not rename internal identifiers just to match display branding.
